gov.usgs.subnetogram.image
Class SubnetOgramThumbnailSettings

java.lang.Object
  gov.usgs.subnetogram.SubnetOgramSettings
      gov.usgs.subnetogram.image.SubnetOgramImageSettings
          gov.usgs.subnetogram.image.SubnetOgramThumbnailSettings

public class SubnetOgramThumbnailSettings
extends SubnetOgramImageSettings

A class to hold setting specific to a given SubnetOgram thumbnail Adding a setting? Yes, it's a bit tedious. However it's all here and it makes everything else easy. 1. Set default if appropriate 2. Create public final instance variable 3. Apply default setting in applyDefaults() 4. Set value in constructor 5. Add variable to toString() 6. Add variable to applySettings() 7. Add variable to getConfigFile()

Author:
Tom Parker
